      en: ["4 cod or haddock fillets (about 180g each), skin removed", "1kg floury potatoes (Maris Piper or King Edward), cut into thick chips", "Vegetable oil for deep-frying (about 2 litres)", "Batter: 180g plain flour, plus extra for dusting", "1 tsp baking powder", "1 tsp fine salt", "300ml ice-cold lager or pale ale", "Salt and malt vinegar to serve"],
